{"tid":237058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷母親錢假鈔混真鈔頂替    女售貨員判240小時服務令","createTime":"2017-05-10T06:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T07:16:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb110d64d2f59d34db641454671640dce4b3e86","tid":237058,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170510/large/1494397579_ce1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170510%2Flarge%2F1494397579_ce1e.jpg&h=47deeee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女售貨員為替男友家人解財困，偷去母親放於床頭的部分現金，涉款3.8萬元，並自製劣質假鈔夾於真鈔中作掩飾。結果母親將整疊現金拿往銀行滙款時被發現內有假鈔而被捕，繼而揭發事件。女售貨員早前認罪，今被判接受240小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n女售貨員符珊娜(30歲)早前在裁判法院承認偽製紙幣罪，主任裁判官羅德泉今指，本案案情特殊，被告偷取家人金錢，可說是出現家賊情況，否則刑責會更大，但裁判官認為案件嚴重，「坐監亦不過份」，終判被告最高時數的社會服務令。<br />\n辯方今求情指被告的背景及社會服務令報告正面，被告犯案是出於意志薄弱，解決問題能力低。"},{"pid":"4b142af1b90e20028d3dfc1722a510b3e4da5a0f","tid":237058,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a391ea53c8d70e96a2c27c82bbe59551c455ff63","tid":237058,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自製偽鈔唔會係打印機印出黎咁on9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫出黎"},{"pid":"588396e297f76699bf0d1d3749ca48a9caeaf979","tid":237058,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"咁貼仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8336e6976d6e94dbf2c451c3f964d84420415579","tid":237058,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁貼仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f37d58740ee136495a752